4. (22, -24): layer 24, bottom side, k=46: (47)² + 6*24 + 1 + 45 = 2209 + 144 + 1 + 45 = 2399 ✔
5. (23, -24): layer 23, bottom side, k=46: (45)² + 6*23 + 1 + 45 = 2025 + 138 + 1 + 45 = 2209 ✔
6. (24, -24): layer 24, first number: (47)² + 1 = 2209 + 1 = 2210 ✔
7. (24, -23): layer 24, right side, k=1: 2210 + 1 = 2211 ✔
